# Hello Android

## Object
Learn how to use Activity, BroadcastReceiver, Service, AIDL, JNI, Intent

## Requirement

Package A :
-	Activity
-	BroadCastReceiver

Package B :
-	Service (AIDL)
-	Print module

1.	Package A : BroadCast Receiver
2.	Package A : Hellow Activity Display (3 buttons, #Java, #Java to Native, #Java to Native to Java)
3.	Package A : Button Click -> PrintHellow from Package B
4.	Package B : PrintHellow in JAVA
5.	Package B : PrintHellow in JNI (Java -> Native)
6.	Package B : PrintHellow in JNI (Java -> Native -> JAVA)
